<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Mercado de Dragones</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Carbón oscuro */
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .navbar-brand {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; /* Fuente vikinga */
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #2c0b0b !important; /* Rojo oscuro sangre seca */
            border-bottom: 3px solid #d4af37; /* Borde dorado */
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            color: #d4af37 !important; /* Texto dorado */
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url('https://placehold.co/1200x600/550606/d4af37?text=Guarida+del+Dragon');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #d4af37;
            padding-top: 6rem;
            padding-bottom: 6rem;
        }

        .display-1 {
            color: #ff4500; /* Naranja fuego */
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #d4af37; /* Dorado */
            border-color: #b8962e;
            color: #2c0b0b; /* Texto oscuro */
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #f3c948;
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            color: #d4af37;
            border-color: #d4af37;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
        }
        .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: #2c0b0b;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #ff4500; /* Naranja fuego */
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: #2c0b0b;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            line-height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 15px auto;
            border: 2px solid #d4af37;
        }

        footer {
            border-color: #d4af37 !important;
        }
        .text-muted {
            color: #a0a0a0 !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
            <i class="bi bi-fire"></i> Dracarys Market
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/">Aldea (Inicio)</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/productos">Bestiario</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero-section text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <i class="bi bi-dragon display-1 mb-3"></i> <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mt-3 text-white">Domestica la Llama</h1>
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <p class="lead mb-4 text-light">
                Bienvenido al mayor establo de los Siete Reinos. Gestiona tus dragones, controla el inventario de huevos y prepara a tus bestias para la batalla.
            </p>
            <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
                <a href="/productos/lista" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 gap-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-book"></i> Ver Bestiario
                </a>
                <a href="/productos/crear" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">
                    <i class="bi bi-egg-fill"></i> Incubar Nuevo
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container px-4 py-5" id="features">
    <h2 class="text-center pb-2 border-bottom border-secondary mb-5">Nuestros Servicios</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 py-3 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">

        <div class="col text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon shadow">
                <i class="bi bi-fire"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-3">Poder de Fuego</h3>
            <p>Clasificamos a las bestias por su potencia de llama y capacidad destructiva.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon shadow">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-shaded"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-3">Escamas Duras</h3>
            <p>Garantía de protección. Nuestros datos son tan impenetrables como la piel de un Furia Nocturna.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col text-center">
            <div class="feature-icon shadow">
                <i class="bi bi-gem"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-3">Tesoros</h3>
            <p>Gestiona el precio en oro de cada criatura y haz crecer la fortuna de tu clan.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="py-3 my-4 container border-top border-secondary">
    <ul class="nav justify-content-center border-bottom border-secondary pb-3 mb-3">
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link px-2 text-muted">Aldea</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="/productos" class="nav-link px-2 text-muted">Bestiario</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-center text-muted">© 2025 Valhalla Code - Forjado en Spring Boot</p>
</footer>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>